## Interface: 120007, 120100
## Title: Vamoose's Housing Decor Guide
## Notes: Track, craft, preview, and acquire housing decorations across all professions
## Author: Vamoose
## Version: 3.17.1
## SavedVariables: HDG_DB
## SavedVariablesPerCharacter: HDG_DB_CURRENT_PROFILE
## IconTexture: Interface\AddOns\HousingDecorGuide\textures\Vamoose_HDG_400_trans
## Category-enUS: Housing
## DefaultState: enabled
## AddonCompartmentFunc: HDGR_OnAddonCompartmentClick
## AddonCompartmentFuncOnEnter: HDGR_OnAddonCompartmentEnter
## AddonCompartmentFuncOnLeave: HDGR_OnAddonCompartmentLeave

# ===== Shared libraries (LibStub + LibDataBroker + LibDBIcon) ================
# Required by HDGR_MinimapButton. Load before Core engines so LibStub is
# available for the other libs to self-register.
